{"tid":2323650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「感謝您為下一代，留下承受一切」","createTime":"2020-12-13T10:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T10:45:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"762e12618d4bf9ba58b08c0d747d2b228499c74d","tid":2323650,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/IBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FIBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=d4e26a08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FIBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y%2F&h=cac23c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/IBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n「感謝您為下一代，留下承受一切」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wdfjd2Y2K9Uxod_Io_8OilBEb6Y=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OV7B3C23RJEBNOENSCQ65VN7D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fwdfjd2Y2K9Uxod_Io_8OilBEb6Y%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOV7B3C23RJEBNOENSCQ65VN7D4.jpg&h=1bf9d6c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一定會守護這裏<br />\n<br />\n【讀者打氣】給黎智英的信繼續寄到本報，來信人為暫時無法張聲的「肥佬黎」申冤，也為香港一代傳媒大亨感到自豪。有女孩傳來親筆信，說一定要守護香港；有女士憑畫寄意，感謝他為這個家的付出。「感謝您一直以來為這個家的付出，為了香港的下一代，您選擇留下來承受這一切。」署名「香港讀者」的一位女子送上一幅由她繪畫的黎智英肖像，感謝他「在黑暗時刻仍堅持為香港燃點起這點光」。親筆信還有來自一位就讀小六的女學生，署名為「永遠愛香港的人，穿着黃衣的女孩」，信中畫了一名小女孩，她感謝黎智英盡心報道真相，她父母每天看新聞都非常生氣，「我不明白為甚麼政府對我們那麼壞，我們沒有做壞事吧！」儘管所有人都放棄香港，但她「一定會守護這裏的」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陸委會轟除異己「港將走向煉獄」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港美麗因為有您<br />\n<br />\n黎生：<br />\n<br />\n感謝您一直以來為這個家的付出，<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：歐美聲援 彭斯促放政治犯： 控黎等於侮辱愛自由的人<br />\n<br />\n為了香港的下一代，您選擇留下來承受這一切。<br />\n<br />\n在黑暗時刻仍然堅持為香港燃點起這點光。<br />\n<br />\n香港之所以美麗，因為有您和一眾堅守家園的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n請保重。<br />\n<br />\n香港讀者上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ITUFTdKocemj6c6WxFfLfafseyo=/886x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MACANT66FRD5XEUEJ4VUQY2WTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FITUFTdKocemj6c6WxFfLfafseyo%3D%2F886x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMACANT66FRD5XEUEJ4VUQY2WTY.jpg&h=4fec60f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G270uZG09FXAidIfULCtvuhT0Ho=/1261x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNIMR2UQSNCGJGZGYD4OQLU2GA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG270uZG09FXAidIfULCtvuhT0Ho%3D%2F1261x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNIMR2UQSNCGJGZGYD4OQLU2GA.jpg&h=ebf5b517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝謝你的付出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TwUt-VR9O2iIpdgtjPY7rGr7y3c=/1304x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TTIVEAAJGJAF3A2JNKQOY4OYM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTwUt-VR9O2iIpdgtjPY7rGr7y3c%3D%2F1304x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTTIVEAAJGJAF3A2JNKQOY4OYM4.jpg&h=2d1ff627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■5歲小朋友Erin親手繪製聖誕卡為黎智英打氣，祝福他身體健康，早日重獲自由。"},{"pid":"40e485cb981609615eaea490dbb9981120998686","tid":2323650,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efb64887512e2d2d1a43e145c3fd22651d0f8d19","tid":2323650,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:32:26.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/f